  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 47a621783cb453147b01764dde5ed130, type: 3}
  m_Name: FinalDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCDialogue
  dialogueLines:
  - It's beautiful...
  - I almost forgot the meadow could feel like this.
  - You succeeded where generations of Moonwardens could not.
  - Not because they failed. And not because they were weak.
  - By the time they understood how fragile the magic had become, most were already
    trying to preserve what little remained...
  - But you arrived at the very end.
  - You were willing to rebuild instead of simply protect.
  - That is what finally saved the meadow.
  - Everyone here is grateful for what you've done.
  - The forest, the spirits... All of us.
  - And no matter how far you wander from here...
  - Moonlight Meadow will always welcome you home.
